cs1302.genlist

Class NodeList<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs1302.genlist.NodeList<E>

  • public class NodeList<E>
extends Object
    A node provides a generic node for a linked list. Each node contains an Object reference and a link to the next Node in the list. All objects in a node must be of the same type.
